    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Stemware shatters on patios, pool decks, and campsites<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">One tip and you lose the glass and potentially cut someone</span></td>
        <td>18/8 food-grade stainless steel — fully shatterproof<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Drops on concrete or tile without breaking</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>White wine warms up in under 20 minutes in summer heat<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">You either drink fast or accept warm wine</span></td>
        <td>Double-wall vacuum insulation keeps wine cold ~2 hrs outdoors<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Same insulation technology as premium tumblers</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Plastic cups feel cheap and ruin the experience<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Nobody wants to drink a nice Sauvignon Blanc from a Solo cup</span></td>
