      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- §9 What is the Stainless Steel Wine Glass? -->
<h2>What Is a Stainless Steel Wine Glass, Exactly?</h2>
<p>It's a wine glass with the same classic silhouette — stem, bowl, tapered opening — but constructed from 18/8 food-grade stainless steel instead of glass. The double-wall vacuum insulation keeps cold drinks cold and warm drinks warm without condensation on the outside. The design went viral on social media after people realized it let them drink wine outdoors without the anxiety of breakage, and the Golden finish in particular became a popular gift item.</p>

